Build-Type:             Simple
Stability:              experimental
Category:               Control

Library
  Default-Language:     Haskell2010
  HS-Source-Dirs:       src
  GHC-Options:          -Wall
  Exposed-Modules:
    Control.Replay.Class
    Control.Monad.Trans.Free.Replay
  Build-Depends:        base >= 4 && < 5
                      , free >= 4.2
                      , transformers >= 0.3

